productivefarming.information.pollen: Use on a fully grown crop to manually pollinate it.
productivefarming.pollen.name: %s
productivefarming.ponder.farm_building.t: The minimum size for the farm is 3x3, corners are optional
The inside of the farm can be any block you need for your crops
Additionally, the farm multiblock must have a Farm Controller...
productivefarming.ponder.farm_farming.te: Crops planted on the farm will be automatically harvested
When crops grow they have a small chance to improve their traits
productivefarming.ponder.fish_farm.text_: If you make your farm taller you can use it as a fish farm
Creatures inside the farm boundaries will be automatically bred and slaughtered
Fish will produce nutrient rich water which can be pumped to a crop farm for increased growth
You can also combine the two farms and have an aquaponics system
